<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Digital Signage Backend</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            background: #10b981;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .info {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .info-item strong {
            color: #667eea;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="status">âœ“ Server Running</div>
        <h1>Digital Signage Backend</h1>
        <p>Your backend infrastructure is set up and ready to use!</p>
        <div class="info">
            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>API Endpoint:</strong> /api
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Health Check:</strong> /health
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <strong>Status:</strong> Operational
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

